gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 104, Cavaliers 91
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Cavaliers, 104-91. Mike Conley recorded 21 points (3-6 3PM), six assists, and two rebounds for the Timberwolves, with Naz Reid adding 18 points, three rebounds, and three assists in the victory. Darius Garland tallied 19 points and four assists for the Cavaliers in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 48-22, while the Cavaliers fall to 43-27.
